== Headline ==

A validator for [[Language:XML]]

== Description ==

XMLValidator is a [[@technology]]; it is a XML-specific validator. XMLValidator relies on System.Xml API to report errors in the XML document. Zero exit code is to be interpreted as successful validation; non-zero exit code as failure.

== Usage ==

To build and execute the validator, you need to have Mono SDK (2.10 +) installed.
Use 'make build' to build the project.

